<verse sid="NEH 11:17"/>and Maththanias son of Micha and Iobeb son of Samoui;<verse eid="NEH 11:17"/>

<verse sid="NEH 11:18"/>two hundred eighty-four.<verse eid="NEH 11:18"/>

<verse sid="NEH 11:19"/>And the gatekeepers, Akoub, Telamin and their brothers were one hundred seventy-two.<verse eid="NEH 11:19"/>

<verse _X_reasonEmpty="verseEmptyInThisTranslation" sid="NEH 11:20"/>&amp;#x2013;<note caller="▼" style="f"><char closed="false" style="fr">11:20</char><char closed="false" style="ft">This verse is empty in this translation.</char></note><verse eid="NEH 11:20"/>

