<verse sid="NEH 11:23"/>because there was a command of the king for them.<verse eid="NEH 11:23"/>

<verse sid="NEH 11:24"/>And Phathaia son of Baseza was at <note caller="▼" style="f"><char closed="false" style="fr">11:24</char><char closed="false" style="ft">Or 'the service of the king for every word concerning the people'</char></note>the king's hand for every word for<note caller="▼" style="f"><char closed="false" style="fr">11:24</char><char closed="false" style="ft">'word for':  Or 'pronouncement to'</char></note> the peopleb<verse eid="NEH 11:24"/>

